[{"ave_id":"AVE-2024-0013","file_name":"2024/AVE-2024-0013.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2024-21683","title":"Atlassian Confluence 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Atlassian Confluence Data Center 与 Server 自 5.2 版本起存在一个高危远程代码执行漏洞（CVE-2024-21683，CVSS 8.8，CWE-94 代码注入）。已通过身份认证的攻击者可通过向 /admin/plugins/newcode/addlanguage.action 接口发送特制的 multipart/form-data 请求，利用新增语言功能注入恶意代码，从而在目标服务器上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Confluence Data Center 及 Server 多个受支持版本，对系统机密性、完整性与可用性均造成高影响，无需用户交互即可被利用，攻击者可借此完全控制服务器。Atlassian 建议用户升级至官方发布的最新修复版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.8,"aliases":["CVE-2024-21683"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2024-05-21T23:15:07.923","updated":"2026-06-17T07:09:58.813","remediation":"Atlassian 已发布修复版本，Confluence Data Center 建议升级至 8.9.1 或 LTS 版本 8.5.9/7.19.22，Confluence Server 建议升级至 8.5.9 或 7.19.22。如无法立即升级，可通过反向代理或 WAF 拦截对 /admin/plugins/newcode/addlanguage.action 的访问请求，同时限制管理员面板的网络访问范围并启用多因素认证以降低未授权利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://confluence.atlassian.com/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=1409286211","https://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONFSERVER-95832","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2024/CVE-2024-21683.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/2024/CVE-2024-21683.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/a6cbad21a8ff006125b5e5b00f9ab42bd00eac7c/2024/CVE-2024-21683.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/2cb2ea94fc4258318a8ccfcb4f378f44a19d8782/http/cves/2024/CVE-2024-21683.yaml","https://github.com/eeeeeeeeee-code/POC/blob/11c00cc5e129cb7d6ed8a99ef1fc108ae83719b8/wpoc/Confluence/Confluence%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-2024-21683).md","https://github.com/gelusus/wxvl/blob/becadd93d7cdff1310246e24c531079026fe8365/doc/2024-05/CVE-2024-21683%20Confluence%20RCE%20%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%EF%BC%88%E8%AF%91%EF%BC%89.md","https://github.com/MrWQ/vulnerability-paper/blob/fcbdb421b62aef6ccac59a1887d94687f4faf9d6/bugs/%E3%80%90%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E5%A4%8D%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%91Atlassian%20Confluence%20Center%20Server%20%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%20(CVE-2024-21683).md","https://github.com/W01fh4cker/CVE-2024-21683-RCE/blob/6d8921bb9966d4a2ff9dfa5b1726c8960023d69b/CVE-2024-21683.py","https://github.com/Threekiii/CVE/blob/b15267648d6c329465c8b4cfbeb7597850ead8c1/2024/2024.05/CVE-2024-21683%EF%BC%9AAtlassian%20Confluence%20%E7%99%BB%E9%99%86%E5%90%8E%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E.md","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2024/CVE-2024-21683.rules","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2024-21683_1.yaml","https://github.com/W01fh4cker/CVE-2024-21683-RCE","https://github.com/absholi7ly/-CVE-2024-21683-RCE-in-Confluence-Data-Center-and-Server","https://github.com/r00t7oo2jm/-CVE-2024-21683-RCE-in-Confluence-Data-Center-and-Server","https://github.com/phucrio/CVE-2024-21683-RCE","https://github.com/r3db34rdh4x/cve-2024-21683-rce","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2024-21683"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2024/POC-AVE-2024-0013.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2024/EXP-AVE-2024-0013.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2024/AVE-2024-0013.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2024-0005","file_name":"2024/AVE-2024-0005.toml","cve_id":"无","title":"AJ-Report 开源数据大屏平台远程命令执行漏洞","description":"AJ-Report（anji-plus）开源数据大屏平台存在远程代码执行漏洞。攻击者可通过向 /dataSetParam/verification 等接口发送特制 POST 请求，在 validationRules 参数中注入可被服务端执行的恶意脚本（如调用 java.lang.ProcessBuilder 执行系统命令），从而在目标服务器上执行任意命令。该漏洞可导致攻击者获取服务器权限、登录管理后台并接管数据大屏，影响面广、危害严重。利用通常无需复杂身份认证，具备网络可达条件的远程攻击者即可发起攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["NUCLEI-HTTP-CNVD-2024-CNVD-2024-15077-YAML"],"sources":["nuclei","cnvd"],"published":"2024-05-20","updated":"2024-05-20","remediation":"立即将 AJ-Report 从 1.4.0 及以下版本升级至 1.7.1.RELEASE 或 GitHub 仓库 master 分支最新代码并重新编译部署；升级前完整备份数据库与配置文件。若暂无法升级，在反向代理/WAF 中拦截路径含 /dataSetParam/verification 及分号后跟 swagger-ui 的请求，禁用或限制 Spring 对路径参数（path matrix）的宽松匹配，并将管理端口仅对可信内网开放，禁止公网直接访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cnvd/2024/CNVD-2024-15077.yaml","https://github.com/vulhub/vulhub/blob/master/aj-report/CNVD-2024-15077/README.md","https://github.com/wy876/POC/blob/main/AJ-Report%E5%BC%80%E6%BA%90%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%8F%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2024/AVE-2024-0005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2024-0429","file_name":"2024/AVE-2024-0429.toml","cve_id":"无","title":"泛微公司Office OA系统 efolioer_in参数SQL注入漏洞","description":"攻击者可通过特殊构造的efolioer_in参数实现SQL注入攻击，攻击者可以读取敏感数据、修改数据库记录、获取数据库权限或进一步攻陷其他系统。该漏洞利用泛微OA的Java JDBC连接处理缺陷，在GET或POST请求中传递恶意SQL语句诱使目标数据库执行，可影响OceanBase等数据库系统。漏洞影响范围广，危害严重，攻击者无需权限即可获取数据库敏感信息，威胁企业数据安全和系统稳定。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.5,"aliases":["HWPOC-2024-05a35621"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2024-05-08","updated":"2024-06-15","remediation":"升级到泛微OEA 10.x系列最新版本，安装官方安全补丁包；更新系统到支持安全修复的版本；加强系统权限控制，限制数据库用户权限；进行安全渗透测试，发现并修复类似漏洞","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1519061/000110465925003924/form8-k_20240509.htm"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2024/AVE-2024-0429.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2024-0019","file_name":"2024/AVE-2024-0019.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2024-33113","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9241,\"outputTokens\":28,\"totalTokens\":10933}}","description":"D-Link DIR-845L 路由器固件版本 v1.01KRb03 及之前版本的 bsc_sms_inbox.php 接口存在信息泄露漏洞。攻击者可通过向 /getcfg.php 接口发送包含命令注入载荷的 a 参数（如 %0A_POST_SERVICES=DEVICE.ACCOUNT%0AAUTHORIZED_GROUP=1），绕过授权验证直接读取设备账户等敏感配置信息。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 5.3（中危），影响设备配置机密性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.3,"aliases":["CVE-2024-33113"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2024-05-06T15:15:23.703","updated":"2026-06-17T07:31:27.160","remediation":"D-Link 已宣布 DIR-845L 进入 EOL/EOS 阶段，不再提供固件更新。建议立即停用并更换为仍在支持周期内的路由器设备。如无法立即更换，作为临时缓解措施：在管理界面禁用远程管理（WAN 侧访问），将管理端口限制为仅内网可访问；修改默认管理员密码为强密码；在防火墙规则中限制对 /bsc_sms_inbox.php 和 /getcfg.php 等敏感路径的外部访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/yj94/Yj_learning/blob/main/Week16/D-LINK-POC.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2024/CVE-2024-33113.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/2024/CVE-2024-33113.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/a6cbad21a8ff006125b5e5b00f9ab42bd00eac7c/2024/CVE-2024-33113.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/2cb2ea94fc4258318a8ccfcb4f378f44a19d8782/http/cves/2024/CVE-2024-33113.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/384d83313f24c48670edc1b1df2f06dc6de4a38c/2024/CVE-2024-33113/README.md","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2024-33113_1.yaml","https://github.com/hack007x/veil_poc/blob/5cfe1da6e975ba816d728597885a5c5e79bda8bd/cves/2024/CVE-2024-33113.poc","https://github.com/zcyberseclab/zscan/blob/8c5a8daeed6afdf16f6945c24a51469d37a023b9/templates/apache/cve-2024-33113.yml","https://github.com/0x727/FingerprintHub/blob/6ee6c869a8c27db6524e9738db3e47a56e0329ab/plugins/dlink/dir-845l/CVE-2024-33113.yaml","https://github.com/jemus17/FOCI-Toolkit/blob/150a60dd4ce6539456b1efbb846ba46cd0e48a73/plugins/D-Link/D_LINK_DIR_845L%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3bsc_sms_inbox_php%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%B3%84%E9%9C%B2%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E_CVE-2024-33113.py","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/6d3a932c05085f06507d23e5a0893fa8fe64ce42/CVE/data/2024/CVE-2024-33113.json","https://github.com/FaLLenSKiLL1/CVE-2024-33113","https://github.com/tekua/CVE-2024-33113","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2024-33113"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2024/AVE-2024-0019.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2024-0012","file_name":"2024/AVE-2024-0012.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2024-21006","title":"Oracle WebLogic Server 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Oracle WebLogic Server Core 组件存在安全漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过 T3、IIOP 协议向目标服务器发送特制请求，成功利用后可未授权访问服务器中的敏感数据，导致机密性受损。该漏洞影响 WebLogic Server 12.2.1.4.0 及 14.1.1.0.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。Oracle 已在 2024 年 4 月关键补丁更新中修复此漏洞，建议用户尽快升级至修复版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2024-21006"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2024-04-16T22:15:14.580","updated":"2026-06-17T07:08:20.627","remediation":"建议立即升级Oracle WebLogic Server至2024年7月关键补丁更新（CPU）修复版本：12.2.1.4.0升级至2024年7月PSU补丁（补丁编号35304436），14.1.1.0.0升级至2024年7月PSU补丁（补丁编号35304441）。若暂无法升级，可在防火墙层面限制T3/IIOP协议端口（默认7001/7002）仅限可信IP访问，或在WebLogic控制台启用\"Enable IIOP\"和\"Enable T3\"为false禁用相关协议作为临时缓解措施。建议尽快通过Oracle Support下载并应用官方补丁补丁包（p35304436_122140_Generic.zip / p35304441_141100_Generic.zip）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.oracle.com/security-alerts/cpuapr2024.html","https://github.com/d3fudd/CVE-2024-21006_PoC","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/2024/CVE-2024-21006.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/a6cbad21a8ff006125b5e5b00f9ab42bd00eac7c/2024/CVE-2024-21006.json","https://github.com/eeeeeeeeee-code/POC/blob/11c00cc5e129cb7d6ed8a99ef1fc108ae83719b8/wpoc/Weblogic/WebLogic%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-2024-21006).md","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/133a0d586d237a236f33d20e243ad929fcf9e0a4/data/2024/CVE-2024-21006-dadvlingd_CVE-2024-21006.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates-ai/blob/d476b10507a31f8cf4e68e148600e8de71a53d49/2024/CVE-2024-21006.yaml","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2024/CVE-2024-21006.rules","https://github.com/oscs1024/VulnIntel/blob/f62012ff68e6011291b2851d1c7ccdb8a587c013/2024-04/Oracle%20WebLogic%20T3/IIOP%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%20(CVE-2024-21006).md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64fd197c5b8f3e4f9493cb07798bdca54583505c/cves/2024/21xxx/CVE-2024-21006.json","https://github.com/imSkows/Cyber-Vulnerability-Analysis-Data/blob/db26c44c5f45c25514223a46675daec7eea03092/data/first/CVE-2024-21006","https://github.com/Vu1nT0tal/yarb/blob/f3ab325ae07c37962fd0266e62c446f77c3c9d2b/archive/2024/2024-04-20.md","https://github.com/lightr3d/CVE-2024-21006_jar","https://github.com/momika233/CVE-2024-21006","https://github.com/dadvlingd/CVE-2024-21006","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2024-21006"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2024/AVE-2024-0012.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2024-0017","file_name":"2024/AVE-2024-0017.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2024-29202","title":"JumpServer 堡垒主机 Ansible 模块 Jinja2 模板注入远程代码执行漏洞","description":"JumpServer（开源堡垒机）的 Ansible 组件中存在 Jinja2 模板注入漏洞（CWE-94），具有后台权限的认证攻击者可通过构造恶意的 Ansible 剧本，在 Celery 容器中触发模板注入，进而执行任意代码。由于 Celery 容器以 root 权限运行且可访问数据库，攻击者可窃取所有主机的敏感信息或篡改数据库内容。该漏洞影响 JumpServer v3.0.0 至 v3.10.6 版本，CVSS 评分 9.9，危害等级严重。官方已在 v3.10.7 版本中修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.9,"aliases":["CVE-2024-29202"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2024-03-29T15:15:12.223","updated":"2026-06-17T07:22:37.197","remediation":"建议立即将 JumpServer 升级至 v3.10.7 或更高版本以修复该 Jinja2 模板注入漏洞。如无法立即升级，可在管理后台临时禁用 Ansible 相关任务执行入口，并严格限制具有 Playbook 创建/执行权限的后台账号访问，同时通过网络策略限制 Celery 容器对数据库及宿主机的访问作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/jumpserver/jumpserver/security/advisories/GHSA-2vvr-vmvx-73ch","https://www.sonarsource.com/blog/diving-into-jumpserver-attackers-gateway-to-internal-networks-2-2","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/2024/CVE-2024-29202.md","https://github.com/Threekiii/Awesome-POC/blob/0f9e22b660cb1ea12c1c3668f9128d93e08da412/Web%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E/JumpServer%20%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%20CVE-2024-29201&CVE-2024-29202.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a23c9152c0ce51f4625e88e1e6abe715ca2d7579/cves/2024/29xxx/CVE-2024-29202.json","https://github.com/eeeeeeeeee-code/POC/blob/11c00cc5e129cb7d6ed8a99ef1fc108ae83719b8/wpoc/JumpServer/JumpServer(CVE-2024-29201)%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E&(CVE-2024-29202)Jinin2%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E.md","https://github.com/gelusus/wxvl/blob/98c7503d2600c12656769211c5fb49a5e292143f/doc/2024-04/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%8D%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%91JumpServer%20%E5%90%8E%E5%8F%B0%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%EF%BC%88CVE-2024-29202%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E9%80%9A%E5%91%8A.md","https://github.com/oscs1024/VulnIntel/blob/f62012ff68e6011291b2851d1c7ccdb8a587c013/2024-04/Jumpserver%3C3.10.7%20Jinja2%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%20(CVE-2024-29202).md","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/da9a3d5ccdbaba095f7b8771822dd7bd866db1c5/2024/29xxx/CVE-2024-29202.json","https://github.com/Simpsonpt/AppSecEzine/blob/5f446fcfcccf21c49b6f4258aeb7ced58439d410/Ezines/530%20-%20AppSec%20Ezine","https://github.com/J1ezds/Vulnerability-Wiki-page/blob/e5e61ef3b30d6c854a6eef982e1ccae251304086/webapp/JumpServer-%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-CVE-2024-29201&CVE-2024-29202.md","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/type/ssti.txt","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2024-29202"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2024/POC-AVE-2024-0017.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2024/EXP-AVE-2024-0017.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2024/AVE-2024-0017.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2024-0016","file_name":"2024/AVE-2024-0016.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2024-29201","title":"JumpServer后台管理功能Ansible远程代码执行漏洞","description":"JumpServer 是一款开源堡垒机及运维安全审计系统，其 Ansible 模块存在输入验证绕过漏洞（CWE-94）。攻击者可在后台通过构造特制的 Ansible Playbook 模板，利用 Jinja2 模板注入执行任意代码，从而在 Celery 容器中实现远程代码执行。由于 Celery 容器以 root 权限运行且可访问数据库，攻击者可窃取所有受管主机的敏感信息或篡改数据库数据。该漏洞影响 JumpServer 3.0.0 至 3.10.6 版本，CVSS 评分 9.9，危害等级严重。官方已在 v3.10.7 版本中修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.9,"aliases":["CVE-2024-29201"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2024-03-29T15:15:11.963","updated":"2026-06-17T07:22:37.080","remediation":"升级 JumpServer 至 v3.10.7 或更高版本；若无法立即升级，可在后台临时禁用 Ansible 模块相关功能并限制可访问后台管理界面的来源 IP，避免未授权用户进入后台构造恶意 Playbook 模板。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/jumpserver/jumpserver/security/advisories/GHSA-pjpp-cm9x-6rwj","https://www.sonarsource.com/blog/diving-into-jumpserver-attackers-gateway-to-internal-networks-2-2","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/2024/CVE-2024-29201.md","https://github.com/Threekiii/Awesome-POC/blob/0f9e22b660cb1ea12c1c3668f9128d93e08da412/Web%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E/JumpServer%20%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%20CVE-2024-29201&CVE-2024-29202.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a23c9152c0ce51f4625e88e1e6abe715ca2d7579/cves/2024/29xxx/CVE-2024-29201.json","https://github.com/eeeeeeeeee-code/POC/blob/11c00cc5e129cb7d6ed8a99ef1fc108ae83719b8/wpoc/JumpServer/JumpServer(CVE-2024-29201)%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E&(CVE-2024-29202)Jinin2%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E.md","https://github.com/MrWQ/vulnerability-paper/blob/fcbdb421b62aef6ccac59a1887d94687f4faf9d6/bugs/CVE-2024-29201and29202%EF%BC%9AJumpServer%20%E5%90%8E%E5%8F%B0%20RCE%20%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E.md","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/50da10c5575a94200ba135d17613df27d01f9b8c/2024/CVE-2024-29201.json","https://github.com/oscs1024/VulnIntel/blob/f62012ff68e6011291b2851d1c7ccdb8a587c013/2024-03/Jumpserver%3C3.10.7%20Ansible%20Playbook%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%20(CVE-2024-29201).md","https://github.com/J1ezds/Vulnerability-Wiki-page/blob/e5e61ef3b30d6c854a6eef982e1ccae251304086/webapp/JumpServer-%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-CVE-2024-29201&CVE-2024-29202.md","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2024-29201"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2024/AVE-2024-0016.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2024-0004","file_name":"2024/AVE-2024-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2024-27091","title":"GeoNode 存储型跨站脚本致账户接管漏洞","description":"GeoNode 是一款地理空间内容管理系统，其富文本编辑器存在存储型跨站脚本（Stored XSS）漏洞。攻击者可通过在富文本内容中注入恶意脚本，当管理员或用户查看该内容时脚本自动执行。由于 Cookie 设置了 Secure 标记无法直接窃取，但攻击者可利用该漏洞获取受害者的 CSRF Token，进而伪造请求修改目标用户的邮箱地址，最终实现完全接管账户。该漏洞影响 GeoNode 4.2.3 之前的版本，CVSS 评分 6.1，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.1,"aliases":["CVE-2024-27091","GHSA-rwcv-whm8-fmxm"],"sources":["ghsa"],"published":"2024-03-27T13:15:47.023","updated":"2026-06-17T07:19:08.667","remediation":"立即将 GeoNode 升级至 4.2.3 或以上版本，该版本已修复富文本编辑器存储型 XSS 漏洞。如无法立即升级，可在反向代理或 WAF 层面对用户输入内容（尤其是富文本字段）实施 HTML 标签与 JavaScript 事件过滤，并启用 Content-Security-Policy 标头限制脚本执行来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/GeoNode/geonode/commit/e53bdeff331f4b577918927d60477d4b50cca02f","https://github.com/GeoNode/geonode/security/advisories/GHSA-rwcv-whm8-fmxm"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2024/POC-AVE-2024-0004.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2024/EXP-AVE-2024-0004.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2024/AVE-2024-0004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2024-0018","file_name":"2024/AVE-2024-0018.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2024-29272","title":"VvvebJs 页面编辑器 任意文件上传远程代码执行漏洞","description":"VvvebJs 是一款基于 JavaScript 的开源页面编辑器组件，广泛用于前端可视化建站。该漏洞源于其文件上传功能未对用户提交的文件类型、扩展名及内容进行充分的校验与过滤，攻击者可在未授权或低权限状态下，将包含恶意代码的脚本文件（如 PHP/JS）上传至服务器可解析的目录下。一旦上传成功，攻击者即可通过直接访问该文件在目标服务器上执行任意代码，从而完全控制受影响主机，造成远程代码执行（RCE）。攻击条件为存在暴露的文件上传接口且目标部署环境允许上传文件被解析执行。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.8,"aliases":["CVE-2024-29272"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2024-03-22T04:15:11.663","updated":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","remediation":"升级 VvvebJs 至修复版本（官方已在 commit c6422cfd4d835c2fa6d512645e30015f24538ef0 中修复），并在上传接口增加白名单扩展名校验、文件内容类型检测与目录执行权限隔离。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/givanz/VvvebJs/commit/c6422cfd4d835c2fa6d512645e30015f24538ef0","https://github.com/givanz/VvvebJs/issues/343","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2024/CVE-2024-29272.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/a6cbad21a8ff006125b5e5b00f9ab42bd00eac7c/2024/CVE-2024-29272.json","https://github.com/awjkjflkwlekfdjs/CVE-2024-29272","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2024-29272"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2024/POC-AVE-2024-0018.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2024/EXP-AVE-2024-0018.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2024/AVE-2024-0018.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2024-0011","file_name":"2024/AVE-2024-0011.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2024-2014","title":"北京派网软件有限公司 Panabit Panalog 大数据日志审计系统 sprog_upstatus.php SQL注入漏洞","description":"北京派网软件有限公司Panabit-Panalog大数据日志审计系统sprog_upstatus.php文件存在严重SQL注入漏洞。攻击者可远程向'id'参数注入恶意SQL语句（如：1 and updatexml(1,concat(0x7e,user()),0)），实现数据泄露、篡改或直接控制数据库。该漏洞影响Windows/Linux平台上部署的Panabit-Panalog审计系统，CVSS评分7.3（HIGH），威胁等级极高。攻击条件较低，无需身份验证即可触发，一旦被披露可被攻击者广泛利用。主要影响范围包括日志审计系统的访问控制、权限管理及审计数据完整性，可能导致严重的安全事件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.3,"aliases":["CVE-2024-2014"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2024-03-21T02:52:26.287","updated":"2026-06-17T07:23:33.743","remediation":"立即对 /Maintain/sprog_upstatus.php 的 id 参数实施严格的输入过滤和参数化查询，禁止拼接 SQL 语句；部署 WAF 规则拦截含 updatexml、union、sleep 等 SQL 注入特征的请求；限制后台管理页面仅允许内网 IP 访问；如无法修复代码，建议暂时下线该接口或升级到 Panabit 官方后续发布的安全版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/mashroompc0527/CVE/blob/main/vul.md","https://vuldb.com/?ctiid.255268","https://vuldb.com/?id.255268","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/2024/CVE-2024-2014.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64fd197c5b8f3e4f9493cb07798bdca54583505c/cves/2024/2xxx/CVE-2024-2014.json","https://github.com/onewinner/Lightx/blob/66baef13ea408675c6c144ae6e01b1df0a9278eb/config/pocs/CVE-2024-2014.yaml","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/bd8147c9eb98061a73ac3211bfcd9edfb4e5605b/2024/2xxx/CVE-2024-2014.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2024/03/GHSA-2c52-g67x-6vf3/GHSA-2c52-g67x-6vf3.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f71c1815da5fc1872d1d999eebe8b28a9e3854c7/SSVC/data/2024/CVE-2024-2014.json","https://github.com/adysec/hwpoc/blob/760f2a0ac5ec983dd84c5e09cb5339a52f81c82b/docs/2024/%E6%B4%BE%E7%BD%91_%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%B4%BE%E7%BD%91%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8panabit-panalog%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E5%AE%A1%E8%AE%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9Fsprog_upstatus-php%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8sql%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-cve-2024-2014.toml","https://github.com/damn77789/nuclei-pocs/blob/81fb60243f8c8e930e9c4f1b65e2110e6e5a9204/folder-3/CVE-2024-2014.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2024/CVE-2024-20148.json","https://github.com/imSkows/Cyber-Vulnerability-Analysis-Data/blob/db26c44c5f45c25514223a46675daec7eea03092/data/mitre/CVE-2024-20146","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2024-2014"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2024/AVE-2024-0011.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2024-0022","file_name":"2024/AVE-2024-0022.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2024-20767","title":"Adobe ColdFusion 访问控制不当导致任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Adobe ColdFusion 存在访问控制不当漏洞（CVE-2024-20767，对应 APSB24-14）。受影响版本包括 ColdFusion 2023.6、2021.12 及更早版本。攻击者可利用此漏洞访问或修改受限制的文件系统，绕过访问控制机制实现任意文件读取或写入。攻击者无需用户交互即可实施攻击，但要求目标系统上部署的 ColdFusion 管理面板可通过互联网访问。该漏洞严重威胁企业系统数据安全，可能导致敏感信息泄露和系统安全破坏。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.4,"aliases":["CVE-2024-20767"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2024-03-18","updated":"2026-07-17","remediation":"建议立即升级到 Adobe 发布的安全更新版本：ColdFusion 2023 Update 7（2023.7）或 ColdFusion 2021 Update 13（2021.13），通过管理控制台「服务器更新」安装 APSB24-14 补丁。如无法立即升级，应通过防火墙限制对 /CFIDE/ 及管理控制台的访问，仅允许受信任 IP 访问，并禁用不必要的管理员 API 接口。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://helpx.adobe.com/security/products/coldfusion/apsb24-14.html","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2024-20767","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2024-20767"],"poc_urls":["https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2024/CVE-2024-20767.yaml","https://github.com/ATonysan/poc-exp/blob/main/AdobeColdFusion_CVE-2024-20767_ArbitraryFileRead.py"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2024/AVE-2024-0022.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2024-0003","file_name":"2024/AVE-2024-0003.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2024-24525","title":"Epoint EpointWebBuilder 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"EpointWebBuilder 存在代码注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 URL 中的 infoid 参数注入恶意代码，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 5.1.0-sp1、5.2.1-sp1、5.4.1 和 5.4.2 版本，CVSS 评分 9.8，危害等级严重。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞，建议用户及时升级修复。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-2024-24525"],"sources":["search"],"published":"2024-02-29T06:15:47.427","updated":"2026-06-17T07:14:34.463","remediation":"立即联系泛微官方获取 E-WebBuilder 最新安全补丁，将系统升级至修复版本（不低于 5.4.3）。如无法立即升级，在 Web 服务器或 WAF 层对 URL 中 infoid 参数实施严格的输入白名单校验，禁止传入特殊字符、系统命令及代码执行关键字，并限制后台管理地址的访问来源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://l3v3lforall.github.io/EpointWebBuilder_v5.x_VULN/"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2024/AVE-2024-0003.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2024-0164","file_name":"2024/AVE-2024-0164.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2024-0164","title":"Dell Unity svc_topstats 操作系统命令注入漏洞","description":"Dell Unity 5.4之前版本中的svc_topstats工具存在操作系统命令注入漏洞。经过身份验证的攻击者可利用此漏洞以提升的权限执行任意命令，导致系统完全受控。攻击者需要本地访问权限，但无需用户交互。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-2024-0164","HWPOC-2024-023e93a2"],"sources":["cve","hwpoc"],"published":"2024-02-12","updated":"2024-08-12","remediation":"升级Dell Unity至5.4或更高版本，参考DSA-2024-042安全公告中的补丁说明进行修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2024-08-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.dell.com/support/kbdoc/en-us/000222010/dsa-2024-042-dell-unity-dell-unity-vsa-and-dell-unity-xt-security-update-for-multiple-vulnerabilities"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2024/AVE-2024-0164.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2024-0015","file_name":"2024/AVE-2024-0015.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2024-23334","title":"Python aiohttp 目录遍历漏洞","description":"aiohttp 是一个基于 asyncio 的 Python 异步 HTTP 客户端/服务器框架。当以 Web 服务器模式运行并配置静态路由时，若将 `follow_symlinks` 选项设置为 True，系统未对读取文件是否位于静态根目录内进行校验，导致攻击者可通过向目标发送包含 `../` 路径遍历序列的恶意 HTTP 请求（如 `GET /static/../../../../../../etc/passwd`）绕过目录限制，实现任意文件读取。该漏洞影响 aiohttpp < 3.9.2 版本，CVSS 评分 5.9，危害等级中危。建议升级至 3.9.2 或更高版本，或禁用 follow_symlinks 并配置反向代理以缓解风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.9,"aliases":["CVE-2024-23334"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2024-01-29T23:15:08.563","updated":"2026-06-17T07:12:37.090","remediation":"升级 aiohttp 至 3.9.2 或更高版本；如无法升级，在配置静态路由时将 `follow_symlinks` 设为 `False`，并在前端部署反向代理（如 Nginx）拦截包含 `../` 的路径请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/aio-libs/aiohttp/commit/1c335944d6a8b1298baf179b7c0b3069f10c514b","https://github.com/aio-libs/aiohttp/pull/8079","https://github.com/aio-libs/aiohttp/security/advisories/GHSA-5h86-8mv2-jq9f","https://lists.fedoraproject.org/archives/list/package-announce@lists.fedoraproject.org/message/ICUOCFGTB25WUT336BZ4UNYLSZOUVKBD/","https://lists.fedoraproject.org/archives/list/package-announce@lists.fedoraproject.org/message/XXWVZIVAYWEBHNRIILZVB3R3SDQNNAA7/","https://lists.debian.org/debian-lts-announce/2025/02/msg00002.html","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52474","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2024/CVE-2024-23334.yaml","https://github.com/BestDevOfc/CVE-2024-23334-PoC","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/2024/CVE-2024-23334.md","https://github.com/vulhub/vulhub/blob/ae581d9cabe832052203eb28ab4690fd73c494cf/python/CVE-2024-23334/README.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/a6cbad21a8ff006125b5e5b00f9ab42bd00eac7c/2024/CVE-2024-23334.json","https://github.com/Threekiii/Awesome-POC/blob/0f9e22b660cb1ea12c1c3668f9128d93e08da412/%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E/Python%20aiohttp%20%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%20CVE-2024-23334.md","https://github.com/eeeeeeeeee-code/POC/blob/11c00cc5e129cb7d6ed8a99ef1fc108ae83719b8/wpoc/aiohttp/aiohttp%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-2024-23334).md","https://github.com/zan8in/afrog/blob/9f792687ed156d63344016f8bf658946079fb494/pocs/afrog-pocs/CVE/2024/CVE-2024-23334.yaml","https://github.com/gobysec/GobyVuls/blob/a5de8e3be10d51a94e0977ecd8086c176251229f/ComfyUI_follow_symlinks_File_Read_Vulnerability_(CVE-2024-23334).md","https://github.com/ATonysan/poc-exp/blob/7ba7f2a08999ace95cc4ab2076c239e10f385dc6/aiothhp_CVE-2024-23334_DirectoryTraversal.py","https://github.com/apache/airflow/blob/df2272c562a7cbf407e405df9c6c82b356a533b9/providers/dbt/cloud/docs/changelog.rst","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/133a0d586d237a236f33d20e243ad929fcf9e0a4/data/2024/CVE-2024-23334-ox1111_CVE-2024-23334.md","https://github.com/jhonnybonny/CVE-2024-23334","https://github.com/z3rObyte/CVE-2024-23334-PoC","https://github.com/ox1111/CVE-2024-23334","https://github.com/wizarddos/CVE-2024-23334","https://github.com/s4botai/CVE-2024-23334-PoC","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2024-23334"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2024/AVE-2024-0015.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2024-0014","file_name":"2024/AVE-2024-0014.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2024-21733","title":"Apache Tomcat 错误信息敏感数据泄露漏洞","description":"Apache Tomcat 存在敏感信息泄露漏洞（CWE-209），当服务器在处理 HTTP 请求时发生错误，Tomcat 会返回包含详细异常信息的错误页面。攻击者可通过发送特制的畸形请求或利用请求走私技术，触发服务器返回包含内部路径、堆栈跟踪、配置参数等敏感信息的错误响应。该漏洞影响 Apache Tomcat 8.5.7 至 8.5.63 及 9.0.0-M11 至 9.0.43 版本，攻击者无需身份验证即可远程利用。成功利用后，攻击者可获取系统内部结构信息，为进一步攻击提供情报支持。建议用户升级至 8.5.64 或 9.0.44 及更高版本进行修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.3,"aliases":["CVE-2024-21733"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2024-01-19T11:15:08.043","updated":"2026-06-17T07:10:02.277","remediation":"建议立即将 Apache Tomcat 升级至 8.5.64 及以上版本或 9.0.44 及以上版本，新版本已修复错误响应中泄露敏感信息的问题。如暂无法升级，可在前端反向代理（如 Nginx/Apache HTTPD）层面对后端 Tomcat 的响应进行拦截与重写，隐藏包含堆栈或内部路径的错误信息，并关闭不必要的默认错误页面作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://lists.apache.org/thread/h9bjqdd0odj6lhs2o96qgowcc6hb0cfz","http://packetstormsecurity.com/files/176951/Apache-Tomcat-8.5.63-9.0.43-HTTP-Response-Smuggling.html","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2024/01/19/2","https://lists.debian.org/debian-lts-announce/2025/01/msg00009.html","https://security.netapp.com/advisory/ntap-20240216-0005/","https://github.com/oscs1024/VulnIntel/blob/f62012ff68e6011291b2851d1c7ccdb8a587c013/2024-01/Apache%20Tomcat%20%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%B3%84%E9%9C%B2%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%20(CVE-2024-21733).md","https://github.com/LtmThink/CVE-2024-21733","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2024-21733"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2024/POC-AVE-2024-0014.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2024/EXP-AVE-2024-0014.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2024/AVE-2024-0014.toml"}]